skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: compliment me
des:
Compliment! is built to give you compliments!
It just praises you!
It just admires you!
No matter you deserve it or not! ( we know you do! )
Use it, enjoy it, smile, laugh and have fun! but don't take it seriously! be humble!!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
